{
  "texts": [
    "The maximum limit considered is 50 frames because of comparatively smaller or similar maximum frame settings adopted in existing studies [59][60][61].The training and validation sets of the combined dataset are used for hyperparameter search.",
    "For each of the aforementioned hyperparameters, a set of three values was chosen in order to manually fine-tune the model and identify the configuration with the lowest loss.",
    "The process was repeated for each one of the four hyperparameters.",
    "The values that composed the set are illustrated in Table 4.",
    "A total of 5 epochs were run to obtain the loss value for each hyperparameter set, as this was the number of epochs that demonstrated satisfactory stability in the preliminary results."
  ]
}